    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Brands (particularly in the real world) would do well to not only use creative copy to convey who and what they are, but use it to communicate how their users can best interact with them and through them. Using copy (and design) to not only sell a product, but craft a series of brand-centric experiences that are thoughtfully unique.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
